title: Allotment Locations
licence_notes:
This dataset was generated from a variety of sources with the core attribute data such as Name, Borough and Organisation being provided by the London Boroughs.

The process of geocoding was carried out manually using a number of different datasets to provide location context. These include Collins-Bartholomew 20k raster mapping, Cities Revealed aerial photography, Ordnance Survey 10k raster and MasterMap.

We do not believe that there are any derived data issues relating to the coordinate information (easting, northing, latitude and longitude) for allotment locations as these were geocoded manually without snapping to any vector information.
